{{Infobox person | name = Anna Faith | birth_name = Ariana Faith Carlson | image = | caption = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1995|11|21}} | birth_place = [[Daytona Beach]], [[Florida]], U.S. | occupation = Model }} '''Ariana Faith Carlson''' (born November 21, 1995), known professionally as '''Anna Faith''',<ref>[https://instagram.com/p/BiGVpXKgb38/"Anna Faith Instagram"]</ref> is an [[Instagram model]] and [[cosplay]]er from [[Florida]]. She is best known for impersonating the character of [[Elsa (Disney)|Queen Elsa]] from the [[The Walt Disney Company|Disney]] animated film ''[[Frozen (2013 film)|Frozen]]''. <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cosplaynewsnetwork.com/anna-faith-top-ten-cosplayer/|title=Anna Faith Top Ten Cosplayer|date=2018-10-08|work=Cosplay News Network|access-date=2018-10-10|language=en-US}}</ref>
==Early life== Carlson grew up with her sister Lexus Grace in [[Daytona Beach]], Florida. Her parents are Jim and Karen Carlson. Her mother created the [[Elsa (Disney)|Elsa]] dress that she wears when performing. She has been publicly performing and modelling since she was in the second grade. She graduated high school in 2014. Her sister, Lexus Grace, portrays the other famous character from ''Frozen'', [[Anna (Disney)|Princess Anna]].<ref name="seventeen">{{cite web|last=Thompson|first=Eliza|url=http://www.seventeen.com/celebrity/movies-tv/reviews/a23537/anna-faith-elsa-frozen-impersonator-interview/|title=Q&A: Anna Faith Explains How She Became An Elsa Lookalike|date=16 June 2014|work=Seventeen|accessdate=28 January 2016}}</ref> Faith became engaged to her long time boyfriend on July 30, 2017.
==Career== She gained notable widespread media coverage in 2014 when she was discovered on Instagram as an Elsa [[look-alike]].<ref name="HuffPo">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2014/06/13/frozen-lookalike-anna-faith_n_5491667.html|title='Frozen' Lookalike, Anna Faith, Totally Looks Like Elsa|date=13 June 2014|work=The Huffington Post Canada|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="NYDailyNews">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/fla-teen-elsa-frozen-article-1.1828726|title=SEE IT: This Florida teenager looks just like Elsa from Disney's 'Frozen'|last=Wagner|first=Meg|date=13 June 2014|work=New York Daily News|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="Time">{{cite web|url=http://time.com/2871130/this-girl-looks-exactly-like-elsa-from-frozen/|title=This Girl Looks Exactly Like Elsa From ''Frozen''|last=Grossman|first=Samantha|date=13 June 2014|work=Time|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="foxnews">{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2014/06/18/frozen-elsa-look-alike-anna-faith-disney-want-to-be-role-model-for-children/|title='I want to be a role model for children'|last=Arnowitz|first=Leora|date=18 June 2014|publisher=FoxNews.com|accessdate=2 February 2016}}</ref> Carlson has been an extra in several films{{which|date=November 2016}}. Besides acting and modeling, Carlson plans to record an album.<ref name="abcnews">{{cite web|last=Rothman |first=Michael|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/meet-anna-faith-carlson-actress-elsa-frozen/story?id=24130119|title=Meet Anna Faith Carlson, the Actress Who Looks Just Like Elsa From 'Frozen'|date=13 June 2014|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=28 January 2016}}</ref> She was invited to attend a royal party in the United Arab Emirates.<ref name="dailymail">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2854082/I-m-living-fairy-tale-rise-rise-teen-model-looks-like-Elsa-Frozen.html|title=Teen model who looks like Elsa from Frozen is now set to make it big with TV offers and modelling contracts|last2=Collman|first2=Ashley|date=29 November 2014|publisher=Mail Online|last1=Klausner|first1=Alexandra|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="evoke">{{cite web|url=http://evoke.ie/extra/elsa-lookalike|title=Teen who looks like Frozen’s Elsa flooded with TV offers|date=30 November 2014|publisher=Evoke.ie|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref> Carlson and her sister have appeared on radio stations, TV shows, and magazines. They have a fan base of over 1 million social media followers.<ref name="wishtv">{{cite web|url=http://wishtv.com/2015/06/26/the-frost-sisters-join-other-cosplayers-at-this-years-pop-con/|title=The Frost Sisters join other cosplayers at this year’s Pop Con|last=Hankins|first=Amber|date=26 June 2015|publisher=WISH-TV|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref> She was named one of the top ten most popular cosplayers in the world.<ref name="therichest">{{cite web|url=http://www.therichest.com/rich-list/most-popular/the-10-most-popular-cosplayers-in-the-world/?view=all|title=10 Of The Most Popular Cosplayers In The World|last=Cramer|first=Rob|date=15 September 2014|publisher=TheRichest.com|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cosplaynewsnetwork.com/anna-faith-top-ten-cosplayer/|title=Anna Faith Top Ten Cosplayer|date=2018-10-08|work=Cosplay News Network|access-date=2018-10-10|language=en-US}}</ref>
Carlson started to branch out and cosplay as characters from other films and comic books, including [[Rey (Star Wars)|Rey]] from ''[[Star Wars]]'' and [[Harley Quinn]] from ''[[Batman franchise media|Batman]]''. Anna has portrayed characters from ''[[Harry Potter (film series)|Harry Potter]]'', ''[[Maleficent (film)|Maleficent]]'', ''[[Cinderella (2015 Disney film)|Cinderella]]'', and ''[[Spider-Man]]'', among others. Carlson and her sister are known as the 'Frost Sisters'.<ref name="thechive">{{cite web|last=Resig|first=John|url=http://thechive.com/2015/12/15/anna-faith-has-broadened-her-horizons-25-photos/|title=Anna Faith has broadened her horizons |date=15 December 2015|publisher=The Chive|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref> Carlson appears at cons and other events, serves as a model.<ref name="Raugust">{{cite web|last=Raugust|first=Karen|url=http://www.raugustcommunications.com/cosplay-the-next-celebrity-licensing-frontier/|title=Cosplay: The Next Celebrity-Licensing Frontier?|date=12 November 2015|publisher=Raugust Communications|accessdate=2 February 2016}}</ref> She was named one of the Top 7 Sexiest Cosplayers in 2015.<ref name="wowamazing">{{cite web|last=Mladenov|first= Mihael|url=http://www.wowamazing.com/talent/top-7-sexiest-cosplayers-you-have-to-see/|title=Top 7 Sexiest Cosplayers You Have to See|publisher=Wow Amazing|date=29 May 2015|accessdate=16 March 2016}}</ref> Articles about her ''Frozen'' resemblance have been featured on Playboy.<ref name="playboy">{{cite web|last=Theodore|first= Nicole|url=https://www.playboy.com/articles/girl-cosplay-frozen-characters|title=This Girl Cosplays ‘Frozen’ Character Elsa Perfectly|publisher=Playboy|date=16 Dec 2014|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref><ref name="playboy1">{{cite web|last=Lemco|first= Tyler|url=http://www.playboy.com/articles/the-model-who-looks-just-like-elsa-from-frozen-looks-just-as-amazing-when|title=The Model Who Looks Just Like Elsa From ‘Frozen’ Looks Just as Amazing When Wearing a Swimsuit|publisher=Playboy|date=13 Nov 2015|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref>
Carlson's cosplay of [[Harley Quinn]] received attention in 2016 when she was compared to [[Margot Robbie]]'s portrayal of Harley Quinn in the movie ''[[Suicide Squad (film)|Suicide Squad]]''.<ref name="goodhousekeeping">{{cite web|last=Escobar|first= Sam|url=http://www.goodhousekeeping.com/beauty/g3479/best-celebrity-lookalikes-quiz/?slide=18|title=Can You Tell the Difference Between Celebrities and Their Lookalikes|publisher=goodhousekeeping|date=20 April 2016|accessdate=26 April 2016}}</ref><ref name="moviepilot1">{{cite web|last=Gale|first= Chloe|url=http://moviepilot.com/p/anna-faith-cosplay-harley-quinn/4108040|title=Anna Faith's Cosplay Does Harley Quinn Like No Other And No, We're Not Joking.|publisher=moviepilot.com|date=29 September 2016|accessdate=30 September 2016}}</ref> Her versatility while cosplaying has been touted.<ref name="moviepilot">{{cite web|last=Gale|first= Chloe|url=http://moviepilot.com/p/anna-faith-cosplay-the-joker-marilyn-monroe/4107245|title=With A Little Bit Of Anna Faith And Magic, This Cosplayer Can Become Anyone|publisher=moviepilot.com|date=27 September 2016|accessdate=28 September 2016}}</ref><ref name="moviepilot2">{{cite web|last=Richardson|first=Jancy|url=http://moviepilot.com/p/disney-cosplay-anna-faith-is-all-the-princesses/4107820|title=Queen Of Disney Cosplay Anna Faith Can Literally Be Any Princess|publisher=moviepilot.com|date=28 September 2016|accessdate=30 September 2016}}</ref> In late 2016 Carlson was once again named one of the hottest cosplayers in the world.<ref name="therichest1">{{cite web|last=Crutchfield|first= Katie|url=http://www.therichest.com/expensive-lifestyle/entertainment/the-15-absolute-hottest-cosplays-of-2016/|title=The 15 Absolute Hottest Cosplays Of 2016|publisher=therichest|date=18 September 2016|accessdate=28 September 2016}}</ref> Carlson was named "Queen of Disney Cosplay" for her work portraying various [[Disney Princesses]].<ref name="moviepilot2017">{{cite web|last=Richardson|first= Jancy|url=https://moviepilot.com/p/disney-cosplay-anna-faith-is-all-the-princesses/4107820|title=Queen Of Disney Cosplay Anna Faith Can Literally Be Any Princess|publisher=moviepilot|date=28 September 2016|accessdate=2 February 2017}}</ref>
Following the release of ''[[Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them (film)|Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them]]'', Carlson cosplayed as Queenie Goldstein in January 2017 during the annual [[A Celebration of Harry Potter]] fan event that took place at [[Universal Orlando]].<ref name="blastr">{{cite web|last=Sagers|first= Aaron|url=http://www.blastr.com/2017-1-31/our-favorite-harry-potter-celebration-cosplay-2017|title=Out favorite Harry Potter Celebration Cosplay 2017|publisher=blastr.com|date=31 January 2017|accessdate=2 February 2017}}</ref> She debuted her new cosplay as [[Wonder Woman]] in April 2017 where she was recognized at [[C2E2]] as one of the best cosplayers to appear at the Chicago Comic and Entertainment Expo.<ref name="kotaku">{{cite web|last=Plunkett|first= Luke|url=http://cosplay.kotaku.com/the-best-cosplay-from-the-chicago-comic-and-entertainme-1794788882|title=The Best Cosplay From the Chicago COmic Entertainment Expo|publisher=kotaku.com|date=30 April 2017|accessdate=1 May 2017}}</ref>
==Other work== She also entertains [[cancer]] patients. Carlson and her sister travel together with their mother and manager Karen for hospital visits, charity events, fundraisers, and schools.<ref name="emirates247">{{cite web|url=http://www.emirates247.com/entertainment/no-surgery-here-meet-anna-faith-frozen-queen-elsa-look-alike-2014-06-15-1.552922|title=No surgery here - Meet Anna Faith, 'Frozen' Queen Elsa look-alike|date=15 June 2014|publisher=Emirates247.com|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="mstars">{{cite web|last=Bellini|first=Danica|url= http://mstarsnews.musictimes.com/articles/32089/20140615/anna-faith-carlson-vs-princess-elsa-photos-meet-real-life-frozen-look-alike-stunning-teen-model-viral-instagram-fame-once-upon-a-time-next.htm|title=Anna Faith Carlson vs. Princess Elsa PHOTOS, Meet 'Real Life' Frozen Look-Alike! Stunning Teen Model Viral Instagram Fame, 'Once Upon A Time' Next?|date=15 June 2014|publisher=MStarsNews.com|accessdate=29 January 2016}}</ref><ref name="fox17">{{cite web|last=Gillfillan|first=Andrew|url=http://fox17online.com/2014/07/09/elsa-look-a-like-visits-west-michigan-child-amputee/|title=West Michigan Child Amputee|date=9 July 2014|publisher=Fox17Online.com|accessdate=2 February 2016}}</ref>
